The network was subnetted into 6 subnets using /27 mask.
Due to hardware limitation (router ports), only 2 subnets were implemented in Packet Tracer.”


GIVEN
	Site address: 201.70.64.0 
	Need: 6 subnets 
________________________________________
🔹 STEP 1: Find Class & Default Mask
	201 → Class C 
	Default mask: 255.255.255.0 (/24) 
________________________________________
🔹 STEP 2: Find Required Subnets
We need 6 subnets
Use formula:
2^n≥6

2^n≥6
	2^2=4❌ 
	2^3=8✅ 
👉 So borrow 3 bits
________________________________________
🔹 STEP 3: New Subnet Mask
	Default = /24 
	Borrow 3 bits → /27 
👉 New mask:
	255.255.255.224 
________________________________________
🔹 STEP 4: Find Block Size
256-224=32

👉 Block size = 32











